window.bookSummaryJSON = "Acclaimed author Jim Lynch sets <i>Border Songs</i> along a 30-mile strip of Washington state and British Columbia. <p>When severely dyslexic Brandon Vanderkool is forced to join the Border Patrol, he learns the border is a haven for illegal drug smugglers and other criminals. Meanwhile, disease has struck his father's herd, and his mother is battling something even more debilitating. Each will have to fight for hope in a world changing too fast.</p>"; 
